00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:19.980
hoe we omgaan met dit vraagstuk.

00:08:20.260 --> 00:08:23.260
De crisis is nu onontkoombaar.

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:27.470
De vraag is: 
